// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-0673 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 39f81389-aa36-50ec-9a36-565fc68c5d43

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:10*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:9*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:18.04*")
